	* GMT_nighttime.cpt:	Colortable for DMSP-OLS Nighttime Lights Time Series
				Designed by Andreas Trawoeger.
	* pstext_func.c:	Reading order of text parameters depends of order on -F option
	* pstext.txt:		---"---
