	* *.c:		Now use mknan macro to generage NaN instead of 0.0 / 0.0.

1993-06-29
	* makefile:	libraries now called libgmt.a and libpsl.a
	* mex:		Routines to read/write grdfiles from Matlab provided in the
			GMT_supplements.tar.Z file.

